1 Pan Private Limited  
User Account Policy  
 
1. Usernames should be unique.  
2. Passwords should be 12 characters, comprising of alphanumeric and special 
characters.  
3. Passwords should be changed every 365 days.  
4. User account should be locked out after 12 consecutive failed attemps.
